257_2fa9.jpg&h=05cdeca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【20:24】有人在商場地上貼上721恐襲相片，和寫上訴求的memo紙等。鍾雅宜攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"db0318f3ac6c3b9618af93d91e497dabdd64dcea","tid":1983018,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200421/large/1587473360_a80f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200421%2Flarge%2F1587473360_a80f.jpg&h=45a18715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【20:48】有人將標語貼在商場中庭。鍾雅宜攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"d8e31e130ebc981902b9b096696e6b5fc89ce37b","tid":1983018,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200421/large/1587476795_61ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200421%2Flarge%2F1587476795_61ff.jpg&h=52e7e314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【21:43】有人在又新街燈柱張貼諷刺習近平的文宣，警員沒有理會。李詠希攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)"},{"pid":"2b17a0c5dae24f96bdb3fb6729a51645a245b431","tid":1983018,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8e31e130ebc981902b9b096696e6b5fc89ce37b","tid":1983018,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200421/large/1587476795_61ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200421%2Flarge%2F1587476795_61ff.jpg&h=52e7e314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【21:43】有人在又新街燈柱張貼諷刺習近平的文宣，警員沒有理會。李詠希攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"黃屍popo <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔愛國<img src=\"/assets/f